But you don‚Äôt have to use Google, and there are many reasons not to. The quality of results between Google and other search engines used to be a real issue, but now you‚Äôd be hard-pressed to find much difference: DuckDuckGo, Bing, AOL, ChatGPT and Brave Search to name a few.
